data.title: What happened to eleventh hour series?
data.meta_description:
The show was cancelled after not becoming the series CBS thought
it would become. After 18 episodes CBS took it off the air losing a
surprising number of CSI viewers as it aired. Personally I like the
show and found that one of the main characters, the male assistant
guest-starred on CSI-Miami on October 5. Its too bad because the
show was very informative, but it probably ran out of interesting
ideas...
data.text:
The show was cancelled after not becoming the series CBS thought it would become. After 18 episodes CBS took it off the air losing a surprising number of CSI viewers as it aired. Personally I like the show and found that one of the main characters, the male assistant guest-starred on CSI-Miami on October 5. Its too bad because the show was very informative, but it probably ran out of interesting ideas...

What is the meaning of in eleventh hour?

Origin: This expression comes from the Bible. The 11th hour is the last hour before the ed of the world. In the Bible, the 11th hour was the last hour of sunlight with the 12th hour bringing darkness.
